The paper is about using deep learning to detect software vulnerabilities, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the use of syntax and semantic information, which are relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with program representations, which are relevant to programming languages (cs.PL).
